title: 820-00165 USB port no data
message: Hello, we have a 00165 that was badly liquid damaged. Repaired all and now everything works accept for USB J4600, it has power but no data. W checked all lines no short, All resistor measure OK and SMC area looks clean.Main spil was around U7100. How to check the data lines of this port?

title: 820-00165 USB port no data
message:
Bypass L4600 is bad.
Also remove and bypass U4650.
